00:35:35,715 --> 00:35:37,076
How did you find out?

729
00:35:37,195 --> 00:35:38,875
I'm doing this for your own good.

730
00:35:38,996 --> 00:35:39,476
You...

731
00:35:40,195 --> 00:35:41,835
