779
00:38:57,516 --> 00:38:58,755
Why is there a fire?

780
00:38:58,875 --> 00:39:01,036
I don't know.

781
00:39:17,556 --> 00:39:18,315
Second Master!

782
00:39:19,516 --> 00:39:20,875
