00:41:51,076 --> 00:41:51,795
Was the testimony

844
00:41:51,875 --> 00:41:53,156
inside the study?

845
00:41:54,556 --> 00:41:55,556
No.

846
00:41:57,315 --> 00:41:58,156
If it were in there

847
00:41:58,275 --> 00:41:59,675
