850
00:42:04,352 --> 00:42:05,990
She made use of the fire
to elude a threat.

851
00:42:06,315 --> 00:42:07,355
It was a ploy.

852
00:42:07,636 --> 00:42:08,476
Young Master.

853
00:42:08,956 --> 00:42:10,875
